sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as RHOAI Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant VLLM_HTTP as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Engine as vLLM Engine<br/>(in-process)
    participant GPU as GPU (CUDA)
    participant S3 as S3 / Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: Model Loading at Startup
        Engine->>S3: HTTPS/443 - Download model weights<br/>Auth: IAM / access key
        S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
        Engine->>GPU: Load model into GPU memory<br/>CUDA
    end

    rect rgb(245, 255, 245)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI API)
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token / OAuth
        Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS | ServiceAccount Token
        KRBAC->>VLLM_HTTP: Forward request<br/>HTTP/8000 | None (localhost)
        VLLM_HTTP->>Engine: Process inference
        Engine->>GPU: Execute CUDA kernels
        GPU-->>Engine: Computation results
        Engine-->>VLLM_HTTP: Prediction result
        VLLM_HTTP-->>KRBAC: JSON response
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 238)
        Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS Protocol)
        Client->>Gateway: gRPC call<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token / OAuth
        Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward request<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS | ServiceAccount Token
        KRBAC->>TGIS: Forward request<br/>gRPC/8033 | None (localhost)
        TGIS->>Engine: Process inference (in-process Python)
        Engine->>GPU: Execute CUDA kernels
        GPU-->>Engine: Computation results
        Engine-->>TGIS: Prediction result
        TGIS-->>KRBAC: gRPC response
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: gRPC Response
    end
